{
  "id": "adv_bond_ktn_01_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……沙季ちゃんはお仕事だし……\n愛ちゃん……意外と、莉央さん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummー… Saki-chan is at work…\nAi-chan… surprisingly‚ Rio-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9299.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "渚、何悩んでるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ what are you worried about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8626524925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "親戚の人からチケットをもらったんだけど\n誰を誘ったらいいか悩んじゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got tickets from a relative‚\nbut I'm not sure who to invite",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9947387854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私で良ければ行くけど\nなんのチケット？　ライブ？　遊園地？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's okay with me‚ I'll go\nWhat kind of ticket? Live concert? Amusement park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.132879718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "行ってくれるの？\nあ、でも、チケットって言っても――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will you go?\nAh‚ but when I say tickets――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7721313635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.6501586119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "生で観ると、凄い迫力だったわね\nお相撲のチケットって聞いた時は、驚いちゃったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually seeing it‚ It was really impressive\nWhen I heard it was a sumo ticket‚ I was surprised",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7001586119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.9848747094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私も初めて観に行くから\n誰を誘ったらいいのか迷っちゃったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was my first time going to see it‚\nso I was worried about who I should invite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9848747094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.1390902996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと一緒に行けて良かった\nだいぶ楽しんでくれてたみたいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was nice to be able to go with Kotono-chan\nIt seems like you had a lot of fun",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1390902996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.7603375594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いい機会だったと思う\nお相撲さんも、あんな大舞台で一発勝負をしてるのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think it was a good chance\nEven the sumo wrestler‚ was having a one-on-one match on such a big stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7603375594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.4818797588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "誇りをかけてぶつかるところとか\nアイドルに通じるところがあるかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Clashing with honor on the line‚\nmaybe there's something similar to idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4818797588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.7431721846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "決まり手？　っていうのも凄くなかった？\n寄り切りとか、上手投げとか、押し出しとか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kimarite? Wasn't that amazing‚ too?\nYorikiri‚ uwatenage‚ and oshidashi…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7431721846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.2347816308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "結びの一番なんて、もう技と技の応酬って感じで\nどうやってたっけ、渚、ちょっといい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Musubi no ichiban was‚ like an exchange of techniques\nHow did they do it‚ Nagisa‚ are you okay for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2347816308,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12365.218369199994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.0436032377
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.7447819551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　いいけど――\n……ひゃっ！？　こ、琴乃ひゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah? It's okay――\n…Hyaaah!? K-Kotono-chan!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7447819551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.1342377663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめん、痛かった！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry‚ that hurt!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1342377663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.5389542182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "痛くはないけど、きゅ、急にハグするから……\nでも、うん、だ、大丈夫、ドキッとしちゃっただけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't hurt‚ y-you suddenly hugged me…\nBut‚ yeah‚ it's o-okay‚ I was just startled",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5389542182,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 20861.045781800003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.5760060549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ハグではないんだけど……\nじゃあ続きね。確か、腰のあたりを掴んで、こう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't a hug…\nThen‚ I'll continue. Definitely‚ hold on to near the waist‚ like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5760060549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.7964
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.7304960807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "（うぅ、いつもは「近くない？」とか）\n（琴乃ちゃんの方が気にしてるのに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh‚ usually she say 'Isn't it close?'）\n（Kotono-chan is care about it…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7304960807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなところでお相撲のマネなんて）\n（いきなり大胆過ぎるよ～……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Imitating sumo in a place like this）\n（That's a bit too brave~…!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2287276507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.8760292292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "な、渚……？　大丈夫……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-Nagisa…? Are you okay…?",
